WEBVTT

00:02:58.737 --> 00:03:01.120
they can be combined in different ways.

00:03:01.144 --> 00:03:05.650
Let's take, for instance,
the particulate matter, the PM.

00:03:05.674 --> 00:03:08.814
It can be a mixture that will include --

00:03:08.838 --> 00:03:10.361
look at the cocktail here --

00:03:10.385 --> 00:03:13.406
soil and road dust,

00:03:13.430 --> 00:03:15.175
sea salt,

00:03:15.199 --> 00:03:16.848
toxic metals,

00:03:16.872 --> 00:03:19.148
diesel smog,

00:03:19.172 --> 00:03:21.414
nitrates and sulfates,

00:03:21.438 --> 00:03:25.584
and all of this toxic poison,
this delicious cocktail,

00:03:25.608 --> 00:03:29.227
is going through our lungs every day,

00:03:29.251 --> 00:03:32.097
and we are constantly exposed
to this air pollution